{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, these domains encompass medical imagery, satellite imagery, botanical studies involving flower images, as well as fruit images, and even real-time image scenarios.",
    "Each domain's unique challenges and intricacies are met with tailored DL approaches, underscoring the adaptability and potency of these methods across diverse real-world contexts.",
    "Evaluation metrics serve as pivotal tools in the assessment of the efficacy and impact of diverse image processing techniques.",
    "These metrics serve the essential purpose of furnishing quantitative measurements that empower researchers and practitioners to undertake an unbiased analysis and facilitate meaningful comparisons among the outcomes yielded by distinct methods.",
    "By employing these metrics, the intricate and often subjective realm of image processing can be rendered more objective, leading to informed decisions and advancements in the field."
  ]
}